Duh, right?  If you're a web designer, your own work should be presented on a website you can be proud of.  Make thoughtful choices site layout, graphics, etc.  Your site should be distinctive enough to mark you as good at your craft, but should also be appealing and accessible to the sorts of people you'll be sending it to. 
